annual production, and the animal rations reported the precise quantity of maize silage fed to each livestock category during the winter period. Consequently, the computation was equal to that used for off-farm silage.", "transport": [{"term": {"@type": "Term", "name": "Transport, unspecified", "termType": "transport", "@id": "transportUnspecified", "units": "tkm"}, "value": 0, "returnLegIncluded": true, "@type": "Transport"}], "min": [0], "max": [101536], "sd": [605], "statsDefinition": "sites", "properties": [{"term": {"@type": "Term", "name": "Dry matter", "termType": "property", "@id": "dryMatter", "units": "%"}, "value": 100, "share": 100, "@type": "Property"}, {"@type": "Property", "term": {"@type": "Term", "@id": "acidDetergentFibreContent", "name": "Acid detergent fibre content", "termType": "property", "units": "%"}, "value": 22.7, "added": ["term", "value"], "addedVersion": ["0.70.0", "0.70.0"]}, {"@type": "Property", "term": {"@type": "Term", "@id": "ashContent", "name": "Ash content", "termType": "property", "units": "%"}, "value": 3.6, "added": ["term", "value"], "addedVersion": ["0.70.0", "0.70.0"]}, {"@type": "Property", "term": {"@type": "Term", "@id": "calciumContent", "name": "Calcium content", "termType": "property", "units": "%"}, "value": 0.19, "added": ["term", "value"], "addedVersion": ["0.70.0", "0.70.0"]}, {"@type": "Property", "term": {"@type": "Term", "@id": "copperContent", "name": "Copper content", "termType": "property", "units": "%"}, "value": 0.0, "added": ["term", "value"], "addedVersion": ["0.70.0", "0.70.0"]}, {"@type": "Property", "term": {"@type": "Term", "@id": "crudeFibreContent", "name": "Crude fibre content", "termType": "property", "units": "%"}, "value": 19.8, "added": ["term", "value"], "addedVersion": ["0.70.0", "0.70.0"]}, {"@type": "Property", "term": {"@type": "Term", "@id": "crudeProteinContent", "name": "Crude protein content", "termType": "property", "units": "%"}, "value": 6.8, "added": ["term", "value"], "addedVer